I'm going to cancel it...

160
00:09:14,166 --> 00:09:17,666
We gotta get this under
control... Got me?

161
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,666
Understood.

162
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:20,458
Oh and, Masa-yan?

163
00:09:20,541 --> 00:09:21,833
