167
00:09:30,625 --> 00:09:31,708
I thank you.

168
00:09:31,791 --> 00:09:35,666
Oh, no, no thanks
necessary... I, uh...

169
00:09:37,916 --> 00:09:38,750
Oh, Takane?

170
00:09:38,833 --> 00:09:40,250
Yes?

171
00:09:40,333 --> 00:09:42,333
Don't forget to take some
flowers by your mother's grave

172
00:09:42,416 --> 00:09:44,250
