174
00:09:46,291 --> 00:09:48,041
All, salute!

175
00:09:50,708 --> 00:09:52,875
Good luck, sir!

176
00:09:54,458 --> 00:09:56,125
Bye, dad...

177
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,583
