ahead of you.

213
00:11:47,875 --> 00:11:50,833
Okay, thanks fellas,
I just spotted him!

214
00:11:52,291 --> 00:11:55,833
Yeah, that's right,
the girls from Tokyo.

215
00:11:55,916 --> 00:11:57,666
Best be careful,
one of them carries

216
00:11:57,750 --> 00:12:01,166
