guns... Handle it.

217
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,833
I'm live at the National Diet...

218
00:12:08,916 --> 00:12:11,000
where inside, representatives
from all branches

219
00:12:11,083 --> 00:12:13,375
of law enforcement and many
concerned citizen's groups

220
00:12:13,458 --> 00:12:16,416
have gathered to discuss
the recent acts of terrorism.

221
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:19,000
Earlier today, Chief Katsu
arrived from Osaka

222
00:12:19,083 --> 00:12:21,333
for a briefing that
preceded the conference.

223
00:12:21,416 --> 00:12:24,875
After the accident, an
anonymous call was received.

224
00:12:24,958 --> 00:12:28,500
What follows is a
tape-recording of that call.

225
00:12:28,583 --> 00:12:30,916
If you got a point, you
better get to it darn quick!

226
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:34,083
